com.affectiva.android.affdex.sdk.detector

Class Face.Emojis

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.affectiva.android.affdex.sdk.detector.Face.Emojis
  • Enclosing class:
    Face

    public class Face.Emojis
extends Object
    A container for emoji metric scores. Emojis are small icons that represent things. The emojis that we support indicate an emotion or facial expression, such as 😡 ("rage") or 😉 ("wink"). Each emoji has a score (a float in the range [0,100]) and a method (e.g., getKissing()) to access that score. There's also getDominantEmoji() to get the "dominant" (i.e., most likely) emoji.

        public float getDominant()
